description: The investment seeks to provide a two times leveraged return linked to the compounded monthly performance of the Wells Fargo Diversified Business Development Company Index. The index is designed to measure the performance of BDCs that are listed on NYSE, NYSE MKT or NASDAQ and that satisfy specified market capitalization and other eligibility requirements.
